ConvertFrom-StringData @'
###PSLOC
TestCimSession =  Testing CimSession to {0} with {1}.
GetReboot = Getting reboot information from {0}.
TestWsMan = Testing WSMan to {0} with {1}.
PsSessionAttemptsFailed = PsSession Test from {0} to {1}: Failed after {2}/{3} attempts. Error: {4}
PsSessionNotEstablished = PsSession Test from {0} to {1}: Not Established
InvokeCommandFailed = Invoke-Command from {0} to {1} failed to return data.
InvokeCommandSuccess = Invoke-Command from {0} to {1} was successful.
PsSessionSuccess = PsSession from {0} to {1} was successful in {2} attempts.
CimSessionAttemptsFailed = CimSession Test from {0} to {1}: Failed after {2}/{3} attempts. Error: {4}
CimSessionNotEstablished = CimSession Test from {0} to {1}: Not Established
CimQueryFailed = Cim Query from {0} to {1} for {2} failed to return data.
CimQuerySuccess = Cim Query from {0} to {1} for {2} was successful.
CimSessionSuccess = CimSession from {0} to {1} was successful in {2} attempts.
WmiTest = Testing remote WMI query from {0} to {1} with {2}.
WmiQueryFailed = Remote WMI Query: Failed to retrieve WMI data, ComputerName: {0}, Attempts: {1}, Error: {2}
WmiQueryEmpty = Remote WMI Query: No Wmi response found, ComputerName: {0}, Attempts: {1}
WmiQuerySuccess = Remote WMI Query: Successful, ComputerName: {0}, Attempts: {1}, Install Date: {2}
TestWinEvent = Testing remote Windows Event Log from {0} to {1} with {2}.
RemoteEventLogSuccess = Remote Event Log: Successful, ComputerName: {0}, Attempts: {1}, Number of Reboots: {2}, Last Reboot Time: {3}
RemoteEventLogEmpty = Remote Event Log: No events found, ComputerName: {0}, Attempts: {1}
RemoteEventLogFailed = Remote Event Log: Failed to retrieve events, ComputerName: {0}, Attempts: {1}, Error: {2}
CimSessionRemediation = Verify the WinRM service is running on the target node (Get-Service WinRM), check firewall rules allow WMI-In and DCOM-In (TCP 135, 5985, 5986), and confirm the credentials have local administrator access.
PsSessionRemediation = Verify the WinRM service is running on the target node (Get-Service WinRM), run Enable-PSRemoting -Force on the target, and check firewall rules allow Windows Remote Management (TCP 5985/5986).
CredSSPRemediation = Enable CredSSP delegation on both the client and server. Run 'Enable-WSManCredSSP -Role Client -DelegateComputer <node>' on the orchestrator and 'Enable-WSManCredSSP -Role Server' on each node. Verify Group Policy is not overriding CredSSP settings.
EventLogRemediation = Verify the Remote Event Log Management firewall rules are enabled on the target node and the Windows Event Log service is running. Run 'Enable-NetFirewallRule -DisplayGroup "Remote Event Log Management"' on the target.
WmiQueryRemediation = Verify the WMI service (Winmgmt) is running on the target node, DCOM is enabled, and firewall rules allow WMI-In traffic. Run 'winmgmt /verifyrepository' to check WMI repository integrity.
'@

